props.title: Custom Airbrush - Packages of 5

props.title: Custom Airbrush Packages: Experience Radiance
props.content: Our Custom Airbrush Packages of 5 offer you the ultimate sun-kissed glow without the harmful effects of UV exposure. Perfect for those who desire a flawless tan, each session is tailored to your unique skin tone and preferences, ensuring a natural and even finish every time. These packages cannot be shared, so you can indulge in your beauty regimen without compromise. Plus, with a one-year expiration from the date of purchase, you have the flexibility to schedule your airbrush sessions at your convenience. Enjoy the luxury of personalized service at Ohana Sun Tanning, where our expert technicians use high-quality products to achieve long-lasting results. Elevate your tanning experience and shine bright all year round!

props.title: Benefits of Custom Airbrush - Packages of 5

benefits.title: Cost-Effective Choice
benefits.description: Purchasing a package of five services offers savings compared to individual session prices, making it a smart investment for frequent users.

benefits.title: Consistent Quality
benefits.description: Receive uniform and high-quality airbrush services across all five sessions, ensuring a consistent look and feel for your projects.

benefits.title: Time Flexibility
benefits.description: With one year to use all services, you can schedule your sessions at your convenience, allowing for easy planning around your lifestyle.

benefits.title: Exclusive Personalization
benefits.description: Each package is tailored to the individual, allowing for unique customizations without the risk of sharing, ensuring a personalized experience.

faqs.answer: No, packages cannot be shared. Each package is intended for individual use only, ensuring that each client receives the full benefits of their purchased services.
faqs.question: Can I share my Custom Airbrush package with someone else?

faqs.answer: Your package expires one year from the date of purchase. Be sure to schedule your sessions within this time frame to make the most of your airbrush services.
faqs.question: How long do I have to use my airbrush package?

faqs.answer: Any unused sessions will expire after one year from your purchase date, and unfortunately, they cannot be refunded or extended beyond this period.
faqs.question: What happens if I don't use all my sessions in a year?

faqs.answer: Yes, you can purchase multiple packages of five sessions each. However, each package must be used individually and cannot be combined or shared.
faqs.question: Can I purchase multiple packages at once?

faqs.answer: Yes, it is recommended to book your sessions in advance to secure your preferred dates and times, as availability may vary depending on demand.
faqs.question: Do I need to book my sessions in advance?

faqs.answer: The package includes a variety of airbrush services tailored to your needs. Please consult with our team to choose the best options for your desired results during your sessions.
faqs.question: Is there a specific type of airbrush service included in the package?
